cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on a new dataset for road scene understanding in unstructured environments, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also proposes a new label hierarchy, which could be of interest to machine learning researchers (cs.LG) and proposes new problems such as domain adaptation and few-shot learning, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
